        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.7</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>New Advanced Mode toggle: "Block chrome://extensions during blocks" (default OFF). When on, a configurable grace period (default 60s) keeps chrome://extensions reachable for extension fixes. Fixes stale-state detection so chrome://extensions can't stay trapped on the block page after a block ends.</p>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 13:32:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>7</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
