        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.6</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>Critical fix: System Settings no longer force-quits outside of active locks (unblocks granting Full Disk Access). Safari &quot;extension tampered&quot; alert now debounces instead of spamming, and missing Full Disk Access is detected distinctly from a disabled extension.</p>]]></description>
