        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1.5</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>Cold Turkey parity (advanced URL matching, pre-made lists, all six break types, dashboard, statistics, device blocks, multi-user targeting), Chrome extension + Extensions sidebar, Date Lock, Locked Block mode, redesigned Block Editor with tabbed layout, launch-hang fix, Sentry + PostHog telemetry, signed native messaging host</p>]]></description>
